               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18200112-124-person1215">
                  CHARLES 
                  READ
               <interp inst="t18200112-124-person1215" type="surname" value="READ"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200112-124-person1215" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200112-124-person1215" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the 7th of January, between seven and eight o'clock at night, I was with the other witnesses, and saw the prisoner and two more watching Messrs. Walkingtons' shop. In about a quarter of an hour we saw one of them take half a cheese and give it to the prisoner - all three ran different ways. I pursued the others, but was thrown down and my hat knocked off. I am sure the prisoner is one of them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18200112-124-person1216">
