                     <interp inst="t18200112-124-person1216" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was with Read, watching the prisoner and two more. One of them reached in, took the cheese off a pile, and gave it to the prisoner, who stood ready to receive it. I secured him with it.</p>
